Hank Worden https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hank_Worden 0 Hank Worden (born Norton Earl Worden July 23, 1901 – December 6, 1992) was an American cowboy-turned-character actor who appeared in many Westerns, including many John Ford films like The Searchers and the TV series The Lone Ranger.
